java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.CellEditor, javax.swing.table.TableCellEditor
public class IntegerGroupTableCellEditor
extends FormattedTextFieldTableCellEditor

Editor which makes use of a JFormattedTextField component for table cell editing, optimized for Synthetica. The editor supports the value types Integer, Point, Dimension, Rectangle, Insets, Color. In case that you want to support additional or other data types simply use AbstractTableCellEditor.getEditorComponent() to get the editor instance and set your own FormatterFactory.

Version:
1.01, 20.09.2010
